OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FPolice have sealed off an entire
OL,7,Fhousing estate - including 19 blocks
OL,8,Fof flats - as they bid to force out
OL,9,Fdrugs gangs and anti-social behaviour.
OL,11,FThe Freehold estate in Rochdale has
OL,12,Fbeen plagued by crack dens and
OL,13,Fcriminality.
OL,15,FNow the authorities have secured a new
OL,16,Fkind of court order, called an Open
OL,17,FSpace Closure Order Zone, which bans
OL,18,Fanyone other than residents accessing
OL,19,Fthe flats.
