OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police say the
OL,7,Fscheme - part of a clampdown codenamed
OL,8,FOperation Affect - is intended to stop
OL,9,Fcriminals entering the estate and
OL,10,Fgathering in communal areas.
OL,12,FThey also want to stop people from
OL,13,Fgathering in open spaces, including
OL,14,Fstairwells, landings, bridges and near
OL,15,Fbin chutes.
