OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FInspector Meena Yasin, who leads
OL,7,FOperation Affect, said: "This is the
OL,8,Ffirst Open Space Closure Order Zone
OL,9,Fsecured by Greater Manchester Police
OL,10,Fand is a revolutionary way of using
OL,11,Fexisting legislation to protect our
OL,12,Fcommunities in the place they call
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,F"The Order allows us to target the
OL,16,Fstairwells and open spaces in a way
OL,17,Fthat will support cohesion. It will
OL,18,Fhelp hundreds of residents and help
OL,19,Four partner agencies."
