OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FThe police said the Closure Order came
OL,7,Fabout after residents told them
OL,8,F"enough is enough" and raised
OL,9,Fcomplaints about drug dealing and
OL,10,Ffacing intimidation outside their
OL,11,Fhomes.
OL,13,FThe policing operation is combined
OL,14,Fwith measures being taken by the local
OL,15,Fcommunity and Rochdale Boroughwide
OL,16,FHousing in a so-called "Clear, Hold,
OL,17,FBuild" strategy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
