OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FThis involves clean ups of public
OL,7,Fspaces, mandatory re-possessions of
OL,8,Fhouses used as drugs dens, and high
OL,9,Fvisibility patrols.
OL,11,F"If we identify people who are
OL,12,Fentering the neighbourhood without
OL,13,Fpermission or to commit crime, we can
OL,14,Farrest and remove them, creating a
OL,15,Fsafer environment for our residents,"
OL,16,FInspector Yasin added.
