OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,F"As well as pursuing criminals and
OL,7,Fremoving nuisance people from the
OL,8,Festate, we are working closely with
OL,9,Fthe local children and their families
OL,10,Fto understand what they want to see
OL,11,Ffrom police, but also create trusted
OL,12,Frelationships with them so that we can
OL,13,Fbetter support the communities that we
OL,14,Fserve."
OL,16,FThe Freehold estate became the focus
OL,17,Fof national attention following the
OL,18,Fdeath of two-year-old Awaab Ishak.
