OL,3,CPolice close off 19 blocks of flats in
OL,4,Cbid to tackle drug and ASBO gangs
OL,6,FHayley Stockham, Director of
OL,7,FNeighbourhood Services for Rochdale
OL,8,FBoroughwide Housing, said: "We know
OL,9,Fthat there is crime and criminal
OL,10,Fbehaviour taking place in the
OL,11,Fstairwells and communal areas at
OL,12,FFreehold, and these new powers will
OL,13,Fhelp to tackle this criminal activity
OL,14,Fand help us to meet our goal of making
OL,15,Fsure Freehold is a safe neighbourhood
OL,16,Fthat our customers are proud to call
OL,17,Fhome."
OL,19,FThe Open Space Closure Order Zone came
OL,20,Finto force on Monday, 4 November, and
OL,21,Fwill last for three months.
